$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_map

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_map -  This method attempts to return the map for the current directory.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mapping query_map(string dir)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^dir%^RESET%^ - the directory to load the information for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the directions mapping
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method attempts to return the map for the current directory.  This
returns a mapping which contains an index being the room and the
indicies are direction, destination pairs.

.EP
